data.description: This home located in the coveted Lake Glen Community.  It is a special one story end unit located on the lake side.  It is a peaceful well maintained community. Enjoy views of the lake from your back patio while sipping tea in the evenings.  This unit also has a two car garage and a private front patio as well.  Call today to see.
